column3: â€œChemmy to the core. Don't come looking for that OG gas/lemon pledge smell. The cut I smoked smelled predominantly of chemdawg and tasted like it too. First time smokers keep in mind this shit sends you into stratosphere when it comes to a trippy head high. Best smoke for a hike through the woods or up a mountain, this is trippy dig into nature" weed to the very core. Rip a bowl

column3: â€œThis is my second time writing a review of Chem OG. The reason I'm writing another review is that this has become my first choice in daytime strains.
